00:21:53.000 --> 00:21:54.000 line:20%
'Delapan..'

00:21:55.080 --> 00:21:56.560 line:20%
'Aku harus menyelamatkan Armaan.'

00:21:59.840 --> 00:22:00.840 line:20%
'Preesa?'

